Package org.intermine.neo4j

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InterMineModelXMLDumper
    Simple utility dump an InterMine model in XML form to standard output.
    Neo4jCompleter
    Complete the relationships and collections for Neo4j nodes that are incomplete, i.e.
    Neo4jEdgeLoader
    Query an InterMine model and load the requested edges (relations) between the subject and target objects.
    Neo4jLoader
    Query an InterMine model, and load it and its data into a Neo4j database, along with the relationships derived from relations and collections.
    Neo4jLoaderProperties
    Simple storage class with methods to return various InterMine and Neo4j services.
    Neo4jModelParser
    Parse a Neo4j-modified InterMine metadata XML file to provide instructions for loading data into a Neo4j graph.
    Neo4jNodeLoader
    Query an InterMine model, and load a SINGLE object, referenced by its InterMine id, along with its attributes, references and collections into a Neo4j database.
    Neo4jSequenceLoader
    Load Sequence residues if they are shorter than the specified maximum length.
    PathQueryServlet
    Handle PathQuery requests by querying Neo4j and returning a tabular response.
    PathQueryTestServlet
    Test PathQuery requests by querying Neo4j AND InterMine with timing output.
